rows.label: qev014302_MSG0001
rows.name:
Ho! Friend has come!
Eliza tell Chacha to expect you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0002
rows.name: Chacha assume friend has come here to make dealings?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_JNK0010
rows.name: Get to the Point

rows.label: qev014302_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Chacha for all the info he has on Alex.

rows.label: qev014302_JNK0020
rows.name: Make Small Talk

rows.label: qev014302_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Chacha for info about himself.

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0003
rows.name: So impatient![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0004
rows.name: Friend is like that noisy girl who follows Eliza around.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0005
rows.name:
Be patient. Informations not going anywhere.
Friend must calm down and listen to Chacha.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0006
rows.name: Chacha been doing informations trade for 50 years![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0007
rows.name:
Network of Chacha best on all of Mira.
Nopon across planet bring Chacha hot, tasty tips.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0008
rows.name:
Tip for friend comes from very reliable source.
Friend should be grateful![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0009
rows.name:
So then! Friend is knowing that someone shot Eliza
and ran like big coward, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0010
rows.name:
Well, friend of Chacha saw same man meet Alex in
NLA to pick up Doll.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0011
rows.name:
When friend of Chacha report this,
Chacha have him follow Alex![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0012
rows.name:
That way Chacha also learn supersecret hiding spot
of bad humans.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0013
rows.name:
Chacha pretty amazing, yes? Product of 50 years
experience in secrets business.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0014
rows.name:
...Speaking of business. Chacha offering whereabouts of
Alex. This very good informations, yes?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0015
rows.name:
Friend of Chacha risked life for this tip!
Chacha cannot sell for pocket change and lint.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0016
rows.name:
Chacha will charge low, low price of 10,000 credits.
Bargain of century, yes?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_JNK0110
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: qev014302_SEL0111
rows.name: Pay Chacha 10,000 credits.

rows.label: qev014302_JNK0120
rows.name: Refuse

rows.label: qev014302_SEL0121
rows.name: Tell Chacha he's charging too much.

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0017
rows.name: Chacha thank friend for business![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0018
rows.name:
Alex in Cauldros, negotiating with smelly Growth
even as friend speaks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0019
rows.name:
Chacha send coordinates to friend so [ST:gender p1=he p2=she ] can go beat
up bad men.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0020
rows.name:
Chacha is also wanting to help Eliza.
Friend must believe![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0021
rows.name:
But this business. If Chacha give away tips for free
and starve to death, then tips die out too.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0022
rows.name: Friend should come back with more money soon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0023
rows.name:
Hoy! Friend is very poor! This makes Chacha sad.
Regardless, no deal.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0024
rows.name:
If friend want to know where Alex is,
friend should get that money.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0025
rows.name:
Well? Has friend decided to buy information on
location of Alex?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0026
rows.name:
Ho ho! Chacha cut special deal.
Only 10,000 credits![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0027
rows.name: Hoy! Chacha thank friend for business![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0028
rows.name:
Alex in Cauldros, negotiating with smelly Growth
even as friend speaks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0029
rows.name:
Chacha send coordinates to friend so [ST:gender p1=he p2=she ] can go beat
up bad men.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0030
rows.name:
Chacha is also wanting to help Eliza.
Friend must believe![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0031
rows.name:
But this is business. If Chacha give away tips for free
and starve to death, then no one have tips.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0032
rows.name: Friend should come back with more money soon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0035
rows.name: Alex in Cauldros. Go there and stop plans of bad men![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0036
rows.name: Meanwhile, Chacha buy fabulous dinner.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0037
rows.name:
Ho! Chacha hear through network that friend has
defeated nasty Alex.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev014302_MSG0038
rows.name: Friend should hurry and tell Eliza.[ST:wait ]
